{"questionId":"26475","questionHtml":"<p>Determine whether the profit is increasing or decreasing when&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><strong>METHOD 1</strong></p>\n<p>(when&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn></math>)</p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>P</mi></mrow><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>t</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn></math>&nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>OR&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>P</mi></mrow><mrow><mo>d</mo><mi>t</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>0</mn></math>&nbsp;(equivalent in words)&nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>OR&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>3</mn><msup><mfenced><mn>2</mn></mfenced><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>8</mn><mfenced><mn>2</mn></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>M1</strong></em></p>\n<p>therefore <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>P</mi></math> is decreasing&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>METHOD 2</strong></p>\n<p>sketch with&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn></math>&nbsp;indicated in 4th quadrant&nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>OR&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>t</mi></math>-intercepts identified&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>M1</strong></em></p>\n<p>therefore&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>P</mi></math>&nbsp;is decreasing&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>[2 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"26475","referenceCode":"22M.1.SL.TZ1.12a","subjectId":"51-dp-mathemati